Introduction

ONEUS is a five-member boy group under RBW. They officially debuted on January 9, 2019, with their first mini album "Light Us".

ONEUS has two meanings: First, the members are united by the power of each fan. Another theme reflects ONEUS's mission to bring ordinary people together to create a unified world. "ONEUS" can also be translated to "One World" in Korean. Their motto is "ONE US! Hello, We're ONEUS" (with making a hand sign of 'one' and a circle for 'earth').

On October 27th, 2022, it was announced that Ravn expressed his intent to voluntarily leave the group in concern of the harm that is being caused to the ONEUS members and fans due to controversial allegations against him and that the group would continue as a five-member group.

On May 8th, 2023, they made their highly anticipated comeback with the song "Erase Me."
